<th class="navbox-group" style="">Presse</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style=""><div class="liste-horizontale">
<ul><li><i><a href="/wiki/La_Petite_Lune" title="La Petite Lune">La Petite Lune</a></i> <small>(1878)</small></li>
